rce_DxSubUnits.cmd:
INSERT INTO $DO_2019_SN_SYSTEM_EDW_STAGING_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT ( CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR,CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_METHOD,CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_TYPE,META_CREATE_DATETIME,META_JOB_EXEC_ID) 
WITH SRC_chargeback_payment_processor  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_chargeback_payment_processor.chargeback_payment_col AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
 FROM 
(Select 'Adyen' as chargeback_payment_col
union	
Select 'Litle' as chargeback_payment_col
union	
select 'Unknown' as chargeback_payment_col) 	SRC_chargeback_payment_processor	) 
,SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	INITCAP(INITCAP(SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG.PAYMENT_METHOD)) AS PAYMENT_METHOD
 FROM 
	$DO_2019_SN_LANDING_BENTO_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG  
 WHERE 
	SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG.PAYMENT_METHOD IS NOT NULL AND SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG.PAYMENT_METHOD <> '' AND SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG.META_UPDATE_DATETIME >= $MP_low_watermark_date 
) 
,SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	INITCAP(INITCAP(SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP.RESPONSE_PAYMENT_METHOD)) AS RESPONSE_PAYMENT_METHOD
 FROM 
	$DO_2019_SN_LANDING_BENTO_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP  
 WHERE 
	SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP.RESPONSE_PAYMENT_METHOD IS NOT NULL AND SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP.RESPONSE_PAYMENT_METHOD <> '' AND SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP.META_UPDATE_DATETIME >= $MP_low_watermark_date 
) 
,SRC_CREDITCARD  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	INITCAP(INITCAP(SRC_CREDITCARD.CARD_TYPE)) AS CARD_TYPE
 FROM 
	$DO_2019_SN_LANDING_BENTO_CREDITCARD SRC_CREDITCARD  
 WHERE 
	SRC_CREDITCARD.CARD_TYPE  <> '' AND SRC_CREDITCARD.CARD_TYPE IS NOT NULL AND SRC_CREDITCARD.META_UPDATE_DATETIME >= $MP_low_watermark_date 
) 
,SRC_chargeback_payment_method  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_chargeback_payment_method.chargeback_payment_col AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_METHOD
 FROM 
(SELECT 'Unknown' as chargeback_payment_col) 	SRC_chargeback_payment_method	) 
, uni_chargeback_payment_method AS 
( 
	SELECT 
	SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG.PAYMENT_METHOD AS chargeback_payment_method
	FROM 
		SRC_PSP_NOTIFICATION_LOG 

Union 
	SELECT 
	SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP.RESPONSE_PAYMENT_METHOD AS chargeback_payment_method
 	FROM 
		SRC_PAYMENT_TRANSACTION_PSP 
 
Union 
	SELECT 
	SRC_CREDITCARD.CARD_TYPE AS chargeback_payment_method
 	FROM 
		SRC_CREDITCARD 
 
Union 
	SELECT 
	SRC_chargeback_payment_method.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_METHOD AS chargeback_payment_method
 	FROM 
		SRC_chargeback_payment_method 
 ) 
,SRC_PAYMENT  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	INITCAP(INITCAP(SRC_PAYMENT.PAYMENT_METHOD)) AS PAYMENT_METHOD
 FROM 
	$DO_2019_SN_LANDING_BENTO_PAYMENT SRC_PAYMENT  
 WHERE 
	SRC_PAYMENT.PAYMENT_METHOD IS NOT NULL AND SRC_PAYMENT.PAYMENT_METHOD <> '' AND SRC_PAYMENT.META_UPDATE_DATETIME >= $MP_low_watermark_date  
) 
,SRC_chargeback_payment_type  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_chargeback_payment_type.chargeback_payment_col AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_TYPE
 FROM 
(SELECT 'Unknown' as chargeback_payment_col) 	SRC_chargeback_payment_type	) 
, uni_chargeback_payment_type AS 
( 
	SELECT 
	SRC_PAYMENT.PAYMENT_METHOD AS chargeback_payment_type
	FROM 
		SRC_PAYMENT 

Union 
	SELECT 
	SRC_chargeback_payment_type.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_TYPE AS chargeback_payment_type
 	FROM 
		SRC_chargeback_payment_type 
 ) 
,  jnr_chargeback_payment 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_chargeback_payment_processor.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
	,uni_chargeback_payment_method.chargeback_payment_method AS chargeback_payment_method
	,uni_chargeback_payment_type.chargeback_payment_type AS chargeback_payment_type
  FROM 
	SRC_chargeback_payment_processor 

 INNER JOIN
 uni_chargeback_payment_method 
ON
(1=1) 

 INNER JOIN
 uni_chargeback_payment_type 
ON
(1=1) 
WHERE 	NOT(UPPER(SRC_chargeback_payment_processor.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR) = 'UNKNOWN' AND UPPER(uni_chargeback_payment_method.chargeback_payment_method) = 'UNKNOWN' AND UPPER(uni_chargeback_payment_type.chargeback_payment_type) = 'UNKNOWN') 
) 
,SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	INITCAP(INITCAP(SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR)) AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
	,INITCAP(INITCAP(SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_METHOD)) AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_METHOD
	,INITCAP(INITCAP(SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_TYPE)) AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_TYPE
 FROM 
	$DO_2019_SN_SYSTEM_ETL_EXCEPTION_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT  
 WHERE 
	SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.META_JOB_EXEC_ID = $MP_prev_job_exec_id  
) 
, uni_chargeback_payment AS 
( 
	SELECT 
	jnr_chargeback_payment.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR AS chargeback_payment_type
	,jnr_chargeback_payment.chargeback_payment_method AS chargeback_payment_method
	,jnr_chargeback_payment.chargeback_payment_type AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
	FROM 
		jnr_chargeback_payment 

Union 
	SELECT 
	SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR AS chargeback_payment_type
	,SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_METHOD AS chargeback_payment_method
	,SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_TYPE AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
 	FROM 
		SRC_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT 
 ) 
,  expr_meta_attributes 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	uni_chargeback_payment.chargeback_payment_type AS chargeback_payment_type
	,uni_chargeback_payment.chargeback_payment_method AS chargeback_payment_method
	,uni_chargeback_payment.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
	,$MP_meta_datetime  AS meta_create_datetime
	,$$AuditId  AS meta_job_exec_id
 FROM 
	uni_chargeback_payment
),TGT_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	expr_meta_attributes.chargeback_payment_type chargeback_payment_type
	,expr_meta_attributes.chargeback_payment_method chargeback_payment_method
	,expr_meta_attributes.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
	,expr_meta_attributes.meta_create_datetime meta_create_datetime
	,expr_meta_attributes.meta_job_exec_id meta_job_exec_id
 FROM 
	expr_meta_attributes 
)  
SELECT 
	TGT_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR AS CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT_PROCESSOR
	,TGT_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.chargeback_payment_method AS chargeback_payment_method
	,TGT_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.chargeback_payment_type AS chargeback_payment_type
	,TGT_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.meta_create_datetime AS meta_create_datetime
	,TGT_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT.meta_job_exec_id AS meta_job_exec_id
 FROM 
	TGT_STG_DIM_CHARGEBACK_PAYMENT
